Author: Luigi21
Title: [ANN] Fittoken the future of the fitness & sport industry
Body: In the past few decades there has been a revolution in technology particularly in the computing and communication sector, and all indications are that technological progress and use of technology will continue at a rapid pace which is already happening.  Accompanying and supporting the dramatic increases in new technologies has been a result of the technological improvements. In today's world, sport cannot go without technology. With the ever growing development of new technologies, they can be implemented into sports. Because technology can give sports something nothing else can, an obvious truth. Blockchain is changing the face of technology, the sports and fitness also are not excluded from this development. Although many people see sport and fitness as a stress, but failed to see it as part of their daily life which is meant to keep them healthy.  But with the latest development of the Blockchain network which is the FIT token, the sport and fitness sector is set to get easier.

Author: Luigi21
Title: [ANN] Fittoken the future of the fitness & sport industry
Body: WHAT WILL MAKE THE FIT APP UNIQUE FIT Memberships (All FIT centres will be able to accepts memberships on monthly or long-term memberships) FIT Day Visitors (ex: Trampoline and Ninja Park; The FIT APP will allow to sell ticket passes for other sport entertainment that is provided at the FIT Centres) FIT Management System (The FIT App Management System be will be provided at no cost to FIT Centre’s and FIT Zones) FIT Exchange (token Holders can sell/exchange their tokens on the FIT App to buying memberships) FIT Private Trainer (The FIT App will make it possible for Private Trainers to advertise their services to FIT Members of FIT Centres and FIT Zones) FIT Sure (Insurance for all long-term FIT members at Centres and Zones; still in process of negotiating with supplier) FIT HEALTH (Track and manage your progress. Take part in FIT challenge and receive real rewards. Work with your trainers on a diet that will be suit the client’s needs) FIT BUDDY (Not the person that want to train alone. Use FIT buddy to join other people who also don’t like training alone end encourage each other) FIT WALLET (FIT will include a Eth wallet address to make it easy to exchange from FIT to Eth and vice versa) FIT TRAINING (FIT will work together in with highly trained professional in the training education to educate and train future personal trainers)  These are the main objective of the FIT APP; but the FIT will not just be for buying membships. Other thing is as well. IF you are traveling between cities or countries, you will just use your app to enter any FIT Centers or Zones without completing forms or need to pay just again. If you have memebrships. Unused memebrship can be sold as well on the FIT exchange; it will be a real unique way of looking at the fitness world

Author: Luigi21
Title: [ANN] Fittoken the future of the fitness & sport industry
Body: 1.Use FIT Tokens at FIT Centers and FIT Zones. 2. Exchange Tokens on the FIT App. 3. All Memberships are in actualy in the form of Tokens. Every time you visit the centre, Tokens are deducted from your FIT app Membership. 4. Unused Memberships (FIT Tokens) can be traded on the FIT APP. 5. Use FIT tokens at any FIT Centre, no need for present yourself, just walk in and carry on. 6. Pay your Personal trainer with FIT Tokens.

Author: tomwalsh
Title: [ANN] Fittoken the future of the fitness & sport industry
Body: Good to see the history of development on the project and investment behind it.  The blockchain is the only source of value to the project and so gives it a platform on which to build from, which offers it some stability.  However the team are too focused on marketing and fitness consulting. You should have set up a proprietary team to work on the blockchain and app and let the marketing and fitness professionals work on establishing and growing the fitness centres. There could end up being a lot of confusion and wasted time with so many people on the team half of whom don't understand the technology.

Author: Luigi21
Title: [ANN] Fittoken the future of the fitness & sport industry
Body: The FIT Token will be used in a few different ways. 1. Token Holders will be able to sell their FIT Tokens on the Exchange Platforms before the 1st center is open. 2. You will be able to use it at the FIT Centers and FIT Zones as payment for services. 3. FIT Token holders will be able to exchange their FIT Tokens directly on the FIT App with Gym Members purchasing products like FIT Memberships, FIT Insurance and FIT Private Trainers service. 4. Unused FIT Memberships Tokens can be resold on the FIT APP. These are just some of the options that will be available the platform will be expandable to other functionality as well. The Main core of FIT is to bring FIT Centers and FIT Zones to areas where the services will be needed. Meaning that FIT can transform any current Fitness and Sport Center that is in need of assistance. FIT Centers will be opening Centers Accross the globe. The Demand for the Token will be that the centers will only accept tokens as method of payment.
